  <entry>
    <title>Excel VBA实现公式自动向下填充</title>
    <link href="/2022/excel-vba-filldown/"/>
    <url>/2022/excel-vba-filldown/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="场景描述">场景描述</h1><h1 id="代码">代码</h1><figure class="highlight vb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs vb"><span class="hljs-keyword">Sub</span> atuo_filldown()<br><span class="hljs-comment">&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">&#x27; 实现自动向下填充公式，模拟鼠标双击单元格右下角的十字柄</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">&#x27;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">&#x27;单元格输入文字</span><br>    Range(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;U14&quot;</span>).FormulaR1C1 = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;发电机转速（r/min）&quot;</span><br>    Range(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;v14&quot;</span>).FormulaR1C1 = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;齿轮箱输入转速(r/min)&quot;</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">&#x27;单元格输入公式，相对引用（可以通过录制宏进行修改替换）</span><br>    Range(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;U15&quot;</span>).FormulaR1C1 = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;=RC[-1]*60/2/3.1415926&quot;</span><br>    Range(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;V15&quot;</span>).FormulaR1C1 = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;=RC[-19]*60/2/3.1415926&quot;</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">&#x27;判断需要填充多长，这里从第30行开始向后循环判断非空单元格</span><br>    i = <span class="hljs-number">30</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">While</span> Cells(i+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10</span>) &lt;&gt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span><br>        i = i + <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>    Wend<br>    cc = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;u15:v&quot;</span> &amp; i<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">&#x27;使用range的方法，向下填充，还有其他功能，可以通过录制宏查看</span><br>    Range(cc).FillDown<br><span class="hljs-keyword">End</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">Sub</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>结构可靠度理论代码共享</title>
    <link href="/2022/Structural-reliability-theory/"/>
    <url>/2022/Structural-reliability-theory/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>11 整理：马文千 [toc] # 1 概率分布密度（pdf、cdf）</p><h2 id="自己编写函数">自己编写函数</h2><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">clc<br>clear<br>close all<br><span class="hljs-comment">% unif</span><br>a=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>b=<span class="hljs-number">3</span>;<br>x=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">3</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">i</span>=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>:<span class="hljs-built_in">length</span>(x)<br>    fx(<span class="hljs-built_in">i</span>)=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>/(b-a);<br>    Fx(<span class="hljs-built_in">i</span>)=(x(<span class="hljs-built_in">i</span>)-a)/(b-a);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">end</span><br>h1=<span class="hljs-built_in">figure</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>ax1=axes(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Parent&#x27;</span>,h1,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Position&#x27;</span>,[<span class="hljs-number">0.1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.4</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.35</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.35</span>],<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;FontSize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">plot</span>(x,fx,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;r-&#x27;</span>)<br>xlabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;x&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;fontsize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>)<br>ylabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;pdf&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;FontSize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>)<br><br>ax2=axes(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Parent&#x27;</span>,h1,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Position&#x27;</span>,[<span class="hljs-number">0.55</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.4</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.35</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.35</span>],<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;FontSize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">plot</span>(x,Fx,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;r-&#x27;</span>)<br>xlabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;x&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;fontsize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>)<br>ylabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;cdf&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;FontSize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>)<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">%-------</span><br>mux=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;sigx=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>x=<span class="hljs-number">-2</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">4</span>;<br>syms t<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">i</span>=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>:<span class="hljs-built_in">length</span>(x)<br>    tx=x(<span class="hljs-built_in">i</span>);<br>    a1=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>/(sigx*(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>*<span class="hljs-built_in">pi</span>)^<span class="hljs-number">0.5</span>);<br>    b1=<span class="hljs-built_in">exp</span>(<span class="hljs-number">-0.5</span>*((tx-mux)/sigx)^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>);<br>    fx(<span class="hljs-built_in">i</span>)=a1*b1;<br>    c1=int(<span class="hljs-built_in">exp</span>(<span class="hljs-number">-0.5</span>*((t-mux)/sigx)^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>),t,-<span class="hljs-built_in">inf</span>,tx);<br>    Fx(<span class="hljs-built_in">i</span>)=a1*c1;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">end</span><br><br>h1=<span class="hljs-built_in">figure</span>(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>);<br>ax1=axes(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Parent&#x27;</span>,h1,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Position&#x27;</span>,[<span class="hljs-number">0.1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.4</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.35</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.35</span>],<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;FontSize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">plot</span>(x,fx,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;r-&#x27;</span>)<br>xlabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;x&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;fontsize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>)<br>ylabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;pdf&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;FontSize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>)<br><br>ax2=axes(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Parent&quot;</span>,h1,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Position&quot;</span>,[<span class="hljs-number">0.55</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.4</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.35</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.35</span>],<span class="hljs-string">&quot;FontSize&quot;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">plot</span>(x,Fx,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;r-&#x27;</span>)<br>xlabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;x&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;fontsize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>)<br>ylabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;cdf&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;FontSize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure><imgsrc="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ma-wenqian/Figure-bed/main/blogs-PicGo-2022/20220320173541-2022-03-20-17-35-41.png"alt="20220320173541-2022-03-20-17-35-41" /><figcaptionaria-hidden="true">20220320173541-2022-03-20-17-35-41</figcaption></figure><figure><imgsrc="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ma-wenqian/Figure-bed/main/blogs-PicGo-2022/20220320173606-2022-03-20-17-36-07.png"alt="20220320173606-2022-03-20-17-36-07" /><figcaptionaria-hidden="true">20220320173606-2022-03-20-17-36-07</figcaption></figure><h2 id="调用matlab自带函数">调用Matlab自带函数</h2><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">clc<br>clear<br>close all<br><span class="hljs-comment">%-----</span><br>a=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;b=<span class="hljs-number">3</span>;<br>x=<span class="hljs-number">-2</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">5</span>;<br>fx=unifpdf(x,a,b);<br>Fx=unifcdf(x,a,b);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">figure</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">plot</span>(x,fx,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;-r&#x27;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">hold</span> on<br><span class="hljs-built_in">plot</span>(x,Fx,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;--b&#x27;</span>)<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">%---------</span><br>mux=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;sigx=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>x=<span class="hljs-number">-3</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">3</span>;<br>fx=normpdf(x,mux,sigx);<br>Fx=normcdf(x,mux,sigx);<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">figure</span>(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">plot</span>(x,fx,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;r-&#x27;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">hold</span> on<br><span class="hljs-built_in">plot</span>(x,Fx,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;r-&#x27;</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure><imgsrc="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ma-wenqian/Figure-bed/main/blogs-PicGo-2022/20220320174416-2022-03-20-17-44-17.png"alt="20220320174416-2022-03-20-17-44-17" /><figcaptionaria-hidden="true">20220320174416-2022-03-20-17-44-17</figcaption></figure><figure><imgsrc="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ma-wenqian/Figure-bed/main/blogs-PicGo-2022/20220320174633-2022-03-20-17-46-33.png"alt="20220320174633-2022-03-20-17-46-33" /><figcaptionaria-hidden="true">20220320174633-2022-03-20-17-46-33</figcaption></figure><h2 id="调用matlab函数抽样">调用Matlab函数抽样</h2><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">clc<br>clear<br>close all<br><span class="hljs-comment">%-----</span><br>a=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;b=<span class="hljs-number">3</span>;<br>ns=<span class="hljs-number">1e7</span>;<br>x=unifrnd(a,b,ns,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">figure</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br>subplot(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br>histogram(x)<br><br>mux=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;sigx=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>y=normrnd(mux,sigx,ns,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>subplot(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,<span class="hljs-number">2</span>)<br>histogram(y)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><imgsrc="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ma-wenqian/Figure-bed/main/blogs-PicGo-2022/20220320175010-2022-03-20-17-50-11.png"alt="20220320175010-2022-03-20-17-50-11" /> ## 课程作业</p><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">clc<br>clear<br>close all<br><span class="hljs-comment">%-----</span><br>mux1=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;sigx1=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>mux2=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;sigx2=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br>x=<span class="hljs-number">-5</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0.1</span>:<span class="hljs-number">7</span>;<br>fx=normpdf(x,mux2,sigx2);<br>Fx=normcdf(x,mux2,sigx2);<br>h1=<span class="hljs-built_in">figure</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>ax1=axes(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Parent&#x27;</span>,h1,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Position&#x27;</span>,[<span class="hljs-number">0.2</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.55</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.6</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.35</span>],<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;FontSize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">plot</span>(x,fx,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;r-&#x27;</span>)<br>xlabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;x2&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;FontSize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>)<br>ylabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;x2-pdf&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;FontSize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>)<br><br>ax2=axes(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Parent&#x27;</span>,h1,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Position&#x27;</span>,[<span class="hljs-number">0.2</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.6</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0.35</span>],<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;FontSize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>);<br><span class="hljs-built_in">plot</span>(x,Fx,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;r-&#x27;</span>)<br>xlabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;x2&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;FontSize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>)<br>ylabel(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;x2-cdf&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;FontSize&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">10</span>)<br><br>ns=<span class="hljs-number">1e7</span>;<br><br>y1=normrnd(mux1,sigx1,ns,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>y2=normrnd(mux2,sigx2,ns,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>y=y1+<span class="hljs-number">2</span>*y2;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">figure</span>(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>)<br>histogram(y)<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure><imgsrc="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ma-wenqian/Figure-bed/main/blogs-PicGo-2022/20220320175543-2022-03-20-17-55-44.png"alt="20220320175543-2022-03-20-17-55-44" /><figcaptionaria-hidden="true">20220320175543-2022-03-20-17-55-44</figcaption></figure><figure><imgsrc="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ma-wenqian/Figure-bed/main/blogs-PicGo-2022/20220320175559-2022-03-20-17-55-59.png"alt="20220320175559-2022-03-20-17-55-59" /><figcaptionaria-hidden="true">20220320175559-2022-03-20-17-55-59</figcaption></figure>]]></content>
    
    
